{
  "texts": [
    "A multimodal large language model (MLLM) then supplies rich semantic descriptions for each region.",
    "Finally, a large language model (LLM) reasons step by step over these descriptions, spatial cues, and scene context to pick the box that best matches the textual query.",
    "The whole pipeline works without task-specific fine-tuning and provides clear, interpretable reasoning traces.",
    "Candidate Generation For the process for generating candidate target regions, an image caption is firstly generated using an MLLM, which we denote as C(I).",
    "This caption provides a comprehensive description of the image content."
  ]
}